==名詞==
鄒語如其他的[[台灣|台灣]]及[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]等之[[南島語|南島語]]一樣，存在著"[[標記_(語言學)|格位標記]]"的架構。進一步、格位標記會和[[類別詞|類別詞]]形成格位標記組而進行其格位區別之作用。比之其它的[[台灣南島語|台灣南島語]]，鄒語的格位標記顯得細膩繁複。<ref>Yung-li Chang ,Chih-chen jane Tang & Dah-an Ho ,"A Study of Noun-class Markers in Kavalan"{{cite web |url=http://thjcs.hss.nthu.edu.tw/english/catalogue_detail.php?id=124 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-03-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007004656/http://thjcs.hss.nthu.edu.tw/english/catalogue_detail.php?id=124 |archivedate=2013-10-07 }},Tsing Hua Journal of Chinese Studies,Vol.28/No.3/Sep.1998.</ref>

*'''e'' - visible and near speaker
*''si / ta'' - visible and near hearer
*''ta'' - visible but away from speaker
*'''o / to'' - invisible and far away, or newly introduced to discourse
*''na / no ~ ne'' - non-identifiable and non-referential (often when scanning a class of elements)

